page.content:
{What is the youngest and oldest dog {you have ever had?} We have had dogs born here;the oldest was 17 years. {Do you have any pedigree dogs?}Yes. {How much does it cost per week to feed {the dogs? }Â£450. {How much does it cost per week for the {Vet.? } Â£550.
{Would you give your dogs to anyone?} No. {What makes a good home for a dog? A person who loves a dog and wants to look after it properly.
